The paper may also belong to the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) as it discusses the comparison of different algorithms for sentiment analysis. 

Information Retrieval (cs.IR) is another likely sub-category as sentiment analysis is often used in information retrieval tasks such as opinion mining. 

Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) is also a possible sub-category as sentiment analysis is a common application of AI techniques such as machine learning and natural language processing.
